<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201031/a6bf7ec6ecb940d98388708a723b879d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>流油溢黄</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">『松哥油焖大虾』</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>勐火油焖 | 啖啖爆黄 | “滋滋”流油</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201031/24ddd355820f454892142cfaf01bea60.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">X</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201031/c5178e533f524519a4d8f10d1fb2ef5e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">／在法律允许范围内，活动解释权归品牌所有／</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>还是个明星收割机</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201031/a6b30b575d994daf9f8f2fc7a5d27cc4.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201031/129c38f05ef646dc9abace07f446634d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">凭借着一道油焖虾就在广州站稳脚跟，还养成了<strong>饭点必排队</strong>的操作，一众明星都为它疯狂打call，连米其林大厨"梁经伦"都打卡过，犀利！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>拥有自家8000亩养殖基地</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201031/0c6677fa86d14ad4873411636ae146c1.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">还拥有<strong>自家8000亩养殖基地</strong>，大虾、大闸蟹每天都打着“飞的”<strong>空运到店</strong>，只只<strong>鲜活生勐</strong>，上桌前都还在“打架”！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>来的人都好这一口油焖味儿</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201031/24ddd355820f454892142cfaf01bea60.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201031/ba6789c9f3234ec8b985a7631c01c79a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201031/7ade7f6e6c1e43cc8fa221dc05e37d60.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">除了食材新鲜，店内的杀手锏就是这由<strong>整整28道工序，</strong>每次吃完都有种要把盘子都舔干净的冲动，尝过一次便流连忘返！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>油焖虾or流油蟹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201031/a791a941bf99472cb14bdfd547f6455a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">正值秋日，除了店内的招牌小龙虾、大闸蟹也回归啦！<strong>均是经典“油焖味儿”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>经典油焖，爆黄虾VS流油蟹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>油焖中号虾</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201031/724bba190fd94d90867c944d6d432cb1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▨ 每只虾都有专人“洗澡”▨ </strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201031/1cbe58b2b3d446aa9e1002c93bfa6c97.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201031/899e69214a0a4b3eace4f3242d218418.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201031/3a8f0fe5b2ec417c98ff4a0e00743302.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201031/b5e9da3ceb5649ca8e4a6d88aad86132.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">在这里，还有一支<strong>专为大虾“洗澡”的“大妈刷虾天团”</strong>，刷虾、去头、开背、去虾线...整整<strong>9道清洁工序</strong>，没想到，一只虾过的比我还好！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▨ 勐火油焖，酱香四溢 ▨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201031/afb61f9210584954834acad2c7753912.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201031/586ba5ba519b46a4bb52e7b22ebdb121.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201031/44c30ffc143d4030a7aab9000ad7a442.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201031/494acaea4b104a12879c0959b3999e1a.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>油炸后的小龙虾</strong>随即进入整锅的秘制酱汁中开启<strong>大火的“油焖之旅”</strong>，随温度的飙升，小龙虾<strong>由内致外的被着上诱人的色泽</strong>，“咕噜咕噜”的沸腾声刺激着五脏六腑的馋虫大动，太馋了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▨ 啖啖弹牙 ▨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201031/0c9c8d8ec3b8421d85d60390371d6309.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201031/afa1c6df78564a76b2278e7ea1c57178.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>整盆上桌</strong>贼霸气！还未入口，一阵阵<strong>馥郁酱香</strong>便即刻袭来，随手剥开一只看着就让人按耐不住！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201031/0a5394e83ede4156bf99be07cc30e714.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>吸饱酱汁的虾肉</strong>一口咬下，满口的<strong>浓香馥郁</strong>，<strong>爽滑弹牙</strong>的口感让整个口腔都在战栗，<strong>丝丝的辣意</strong>在舌尖流转，超满足！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201031/e163b3a78c564aa984b64c2774a059df.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201031/e1de56da61654ffaa32f9f823fcaf6ed.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201031/1961939ec15f4047a27692d2ed167171.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">面对这<strong>喷香诱人的Q弹虾肉</strong>，还顾及什么靓仔靓女的形象，左右开弓一口接一口、虾肉串串大口吃，<strong>微辣鲜香</strong>根本停不下来！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>油焖大闸蟹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▨ 精选多黄母蟹 ▨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201031/6aa7cda150cb480fb9967d2f701714c7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">每一只都是<strong>精心挑选的多黄母蟹</strong>，打开蟹壳的那一刻有被<strong>金灿灿的蟹黄</strong>震惊到</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▨ 勐火油焖，酥香扑鼻 ▨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201031/fce555e8b70343a4918ec5baa16595f9.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201031/ef0c903d4fd048b6a40d259de5541222.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">相较于虾，同样的焖煮方法，酱香丰盈的同时<strong>更多了一份属于蟹的清香</strong>！在秘制酱汁中“泡温泉”的<strong>大闸蟹每一只都吸饱了味</strong>，站在厨房外都能被它诱人的香味撩拨的坐立不安~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▨ 只只流油又溢黄 ▨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201031/f67a753a24064456ba0c3ebbfa0c33a4.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201031/a8eeb857d38d4fafa1ad3c1e3effd5dc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">打开蟹壳，<strong>内里满满蟹黄直接怼你脸上</strong>，就差溢出屏幕了！暴力的对半掰开，还会<strong>“滋滋”的往外冒油</strong>，香气扑鼻、浓香四溢，超治愈~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201031/a6bf7ec6ecb940d98388708a723b879d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201031/3c49026300b242628d98eb0572977b81.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201031/6bd25ec01a4f4f7cb8559f9e11ccb1a6.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">历经酱汁浸润的大闸蟹，<strong>蟹黄浓香、蟹肉鲜甜、酱汁丰盈</strong>，多种风味轮番在口腔中轰炸，直叫人缴械投降，<strong>咸香微辣的爽感</strong>直冲天灵盖！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>还得加上这些才过瘾</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>金牌凉面</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201031/9987047eab6346e3b53e429d75480427.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">作为油焖虾好搭档的它<strong>!</strong>淋上秘制麻酱，<strong>面条爽滑有嚼劲</strong>，大口撩起嗦着吃！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201031/6a1a922dbfab458d96a9d3c0668d4194.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201031/8db77359d8904243ad7b0a267c959c85.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201031/471a3cd00f7b4ca1ab4609bb0c9690ed.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">加入油焖虾肉，面条在疯狂捞拌中瞬间被赋予另一种酱香风味，仿佛打开了新世界大门！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>长沙臭豆腐</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201031/727bfeff348d425ebf4af25e4f71e5c6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">新鲜热辣的臭豆腐，<strong>外层被炸至焦酥</strong>，<strong>内里却是惊喜的滑嫩</strong>，一口一个hit满足，绝对值得一试~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201031/214f35be50404c53875e530503878ef4.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一口咬下，还会<strong>“滋啦”喷汁</strong>，饱满的汁水在口腔中激荡环绕,超nice~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>绝味毛豆</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201031/c52b68e43e734bcab181b979fe315df2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">都喝上啤酒了，<strong>香香辣辣的毛豆</strong>又怎能少，越嚼越香越上头，着实很绝味！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201031/b2560a70190f4ea3800d904b34e4463e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201031/8e7d6704f3834bea9da3a4f441f6bd0d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201031/a160c1f77bee4b788a2d1ae3262b74f3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201031/eb654cbb00024e15bbe2bf154900210e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>明亮宽敞的环境</strong>，暖黄的色调让人进店就卸下疲惫</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201031/fc8d04e16ca9493a996130297916b5b9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">／在法律允许范围内，活动解释权归品牌所有／</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201031/8afd982d3dda4e3b861de1bd904245af.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
