<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>原叶茶汤，鲜奶现冲『国潮奶茶』</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">／在法律允许范围内，活动解释权归品牌所有／</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>01</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201031/aca87cc558324b979d7476279205bdd4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201031/3530df61ab244dba9f17e8ced0d381c5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201031/5c943daacefc4441a232ba954eebd597.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201031/f2c7488ef898434782d7cf1ab6679c02.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>嫣雨柠茶四大招牌，闭着眼点都不会出错！</strong>淡雅的桃香乌龙柠檬茶、清新回甘的鸭屎香柠茶、浓郁酸涩的鸳鸯柠檬茶和甜而不腻的嫣雨乌龙！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201031/4f60649034f84eb08d2e56310913a628.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>02</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">桃香柠檬茶</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201031/453d299767b3470391b4805cdb35921e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">带有桃香味的柠檬茶，今年的热门选手！<strong>桃香柠檬茶，柠檬果酸和乌龙茶的甘醇，喝起来不会甜腻。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>- 原叶冲泡 -</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201031/4efbf33188cc45b2ae22a05370d5a838.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">柠檬茶<strong>茶底全是原叶冲泡</strong>，保证了茶叶天然的味感。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>- 新鲜柠檬&amp;琥珀茶汤 -</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201031/3bc685f33cf04d77b89e45cc24def996.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201031/593f4f2351ac409399313e353b6d2ea9.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201031/ba3efda54e754a72b76f37aecafc349f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">每一片柠檬都保持在了5mm的厚度，经过30+次的锤，冲上既有醇厚甘甜的乌龙茶味，又有浓郁的白桃果香的茶汤，<strong>口感更加淡雅清甜</strong>！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>- 大力出奇迹 -</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201031/cff8f8d9fcca4e458c3a05b13a0ed02a.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201031/d89bde50358840be94bd62b5ffccadc3.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">小哥的肌肉在隐隐的暴起青筋，果然这样才能充分的让味道融合！然后倒入冰块，一杯清爽的桃香柠檬茶就完成了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>“小剧场”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201031/8337f4239fbd464a95a6bbe9cdf15831.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>biu~biu 变变变</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>03</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>- 嫣雨乌龙 -</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201031/38777b38983c47c7bf279ec3d6ccc06d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201031/ad6e0d8200064fed89829cb59185d68f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201031/2fcf6000cff3415d897427ec2d77f82f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">店内另一款必点招牌！采用白桃乌龙茶，搭配雀巢全脂牛奶，<strong>入口顺滑，清香四溢，有白桃乌龙茶底的香味</strong>，我可以再来一杯！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201031/72657860165e45738c266ab05a1f5c42.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>拿到手后，打开盖子，轻抿一口，享受细腻的奶泡</strong>，再慢慢喝到奶茶，甜而不腻，这种奶茶，多喝都不会胖，所以我要再来一杯！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">第二种喝法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201031/12279fcdf8a845819ee8df44e1e2f9fb.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201031/a343bbdfa7cf47a0b68b19521f03eefe.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">&lt;&lt;&lt;</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201031/13ddfca21f75471bb59f9aa48f386fee.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">顶层加入新西兰安佳奶油打发后的轻柔忌廉，<strong>厚厚一层的忌廉，轻盈顺滑</strong>，加上香脆的碧根果点缀，奶香浓郁，口感丰富！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>- 鸭屎香柠茶 -</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201031/96db60344aeb48d0ba98bc2308b0ffa6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">选用了正宗的鸭屎香茶叶，入口顺滑清爽不腻，香而不涩，<strong>手工锤新鲜柠檬后，醇香的茶底透着两种柠檬的清香</strong>，喝完以后喉咙会有悠长的回甘！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>- 鸳鸯柠檬茶 -</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201031/87b2f1a13ce44339ba6893d7de135d09.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201031/46ce6fa318ab49848da956bf83fca2e8.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这款适合<strong>“柠檬茶骨灰级爱好者”</strong>！黄柠檬和青柠檬的搭配着红汤的涩，<strong>口感会更浓郁酸涩</strong>！很适合那些嗜酸星人！其中，就我这个“老柠檬精”！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>04</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>- 国潮饮品店 -</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201031/9f5a86c0bf0f45eda93e7c724714b222.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201031/83ea2ea4d7f44552b88738a3d749a4bf.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>&lt;&lt;&lt; &lt;&lt;&lt; &lt;&lt;&lt;</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>&lt;&lt;&lt; &lt;&lt;&lt; &lt;&lt;&lt;</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201031/339cfcdcb3eb44ac9b0e617b2785ef00.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">古风的环境，店内桃花和印在墙上的古词，将<strong>中国传统元素与新式茶饮结合</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>- 打卡港风照片 -</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201031/30d8762f4c3f4f6abed87265ad524d85.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这条以港式风味为主的街道，神还原香港的街道，有电话亭、计程车、彩虹椅、巴士站等复古道具，满满港风，<strong>拿着柠檬茶随便凹造型，轻松都hold的住！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>- 打卡IN风照片 -</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201031/ed4074a36e0044b3be494b3516def0e1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">在楼梯上打卡一张，拍摄到后面的全景，IN风马上就能get！<strong>就在巴士站上面的楼梯，这个取景点必须疯狂安利给你们！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>- 打卡质感票圈大片 -</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201031/0ff39e8dbbab4f47b5bd7f1c1e5ddeb7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">坐在斑马线上，背景就是复古的士，喝着柠檬茶，闭眼浅笑。</p>
