<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>◈酸菜鱼+榴莲，你敢试吗◈</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>榴莲忘返酸菜鱼</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201031/e5e0e9836b404294a8e7e694d8d35c64.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▨ 新鲜鲈鱼 ▨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201031/57318b42f2e745c8aa59fb8f2b6712a8.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">选用的是鲈鱼，肉质滑嫩，每天新鲜到店，活蹦乱跳</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▨ 3mm薄的鱼片 ▨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201031/eb78c067e6464e7ba87acd7931f49713.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">///</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201031/aa1027fc48e74629aa9d86977a735621.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">酸菜鱼的最大杀器那绝对的是鱼肉！师傅刀工了得，又快又稳！片成<strong>3mm的鱼片</strong>，每片鱼肉都非常薄，还微微透光。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▨ 酸菜要腌制1个月 ▨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201031/4e511a034f43435da121a9b46974b1c6.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201031/b57c139940d847a7b89acc1c20146707.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">自家腌制的脆嫩酸菜要<strong>足足腌制1个月</strong>，经过老坛泡制发酵后更加酸爽！每一块都<strong>爽脆无比</strong>。再经过翻炒过后，牢牢将酸味锁住，整道菜也会更加入味。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▨ 大半斤榴莲入汤 ▨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201031/82fb90316fec47d0b4f00e40f8eab5d6.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201031/60392bebd4b6470aa6bda1051aa7995b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">放入<strong>大半斤的泰国金枕榴莲肉</strong>，让酸菜和榴莲的味道融合，让整个汤味更加香浓。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▨ 酸菜鱼要这样吃 ▨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201031/2320707696a1408f99f798c2f2b02e38.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>① 先来一碗鲜香鱼汤</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201031/276520692d0640f08c2a8bd878217319.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>② 鱼肉要和酸菜一起吃</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201031/cfdffcbfc5194249bfb12e4ef5f66c34.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>③ 配上米饭吃太香了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">打开酸菜鱼的正确吃法：<strong>喝汤</strong>、<strong>吃肉</strong>、<strong>配饭</strong>，鱼鲜汤更鲜~而且榴莲放进酸菜鱼里味道其实并不违和，整个汤反而香味更浓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201031/fb29f34658b943c4a134d6630feb73b3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">看似黑暗料理，但是这样大胆创新的尝试反而吸引了一众回头客，鱼肉<strong>其实带着榴莲的甜味</strong>，一点儿也不臭，反而真香！每片鱼肉都充分吸收了酸菜的酸和榴莲的甜，嫩滑多汁、鲜香爽口，连不吃榴莲的人都大喊着：真香！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>三生三世酸菜鱼</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201031/85b3534ef4a244649ac1c1b6bea28236.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201031/edc5ebcddb6f477ba51243906f3700b3.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">如果还是接受不了榴莲酸菜鱼的朋友，那就来一份他们家经典的招牌——<strong>三生三世酸菜鱼</strong>！加了酸菜之外还加了柠檬片，提升酸劲儿，同时让着整个口味更加清新~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▨ 辣味升级，油泼入味 ▨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201031/64331dc089ea4149a0c0896c5124f142.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201031/72ecfadbad444d9986e84b70e311b351.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这道经典口味用传统油泼，选用四川当地的花椒和辣椒，相较在下整个口味更加咸香，香辣味也会更加浓郁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201031/733187f251ff45db9aaffdbc9fb37c2a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>◈这些川菜小吃◈</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>香辣虾拼牛蛙</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201031/dabd0d84d25d48348ff1e5e848550d43.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>香辣虾拼牛蛙</strong>超大一份一上桌就勾得我直流口水，让人忍不住想动筷子！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201031/a0d10adfc5a744379e7ebadc6929732e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201031/0e56121a84064d1fa1a5f0e9b383378c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201031/a267bc61bd0d4adc88c3103037def2b0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">加上花椒和辣椒，正宗地川渝口味~整个满满一份都是虾和牛蛙，每一块肉都非常厚实。外焦里嫩，酥香可口~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>口水鸡</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201031/48c8ba78e0f94c2f81544a87034288d1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>//</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201031/ea2ac60fa28d4ae5b96404c010b835c8.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">麻辣红油川味，入口口水分泌的更加疯狂，名副其实“口水鸡”，让你吃完一块忍不住还想再来一块！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>老少咸宜</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▨ 老成都串串 ▨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201031/a6ea2e2d3191412182391c26a6e1ce9e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">地道的<strong>老成都串串</strong>，有毛肚、鸭血、脆皮肠十几种的串让你一次尝个够，一串就到老成都街头！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201031/33c78dbfbedb46eeb1da97e93ee50519.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">在这里，边吃鱼边撸串，川渝江湖口味一次吃过瘾！这道串串爱川渝油碟风味的千万不能错过！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▨ 白玉菇炒鱼肚 ▨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201031/9ff27fa14bee4bcc8538d33e2d740057.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这道<strong>白玉菇炒鱼肚</strong>，QQ弹弹的鱼肚处理得很干净，没有一点儿腥味，和白玉菇搭配起来，是家的味道啊~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▨ 青桔海蜇丝&amp;豆浆一锅鲜 ▨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201031/280d607142ee45808373daae9fc7cb84.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201031/bf8c4c4b498f4b5a9e640414fbf71b7b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>青桔海蜇丝</strong>和<strong>豆浆一锅鲜</strong>，都是创新菜式，超适合不能吃辣的小伙伴~清新的海蜇丝吃起来卜卜脆，一锅鲜里午餐肉、鲜虾、白贝料多到抵！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▨ 麻婆豆腐 ▨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201031/164af492aa5848a68d0b12fb651b1486.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201031/e4bb8f2eaf2c4070a83b991a0decfba7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>///</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201031/0bd54dc099f1431681592e10e022aec3.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">味道也hin好，光这一份拌饭吃，我能干掉3份米饭！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▨ 桃花冰粉&amp;桃花酿 ▨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201031/c7924a4e3ccd410da5f20f68a5ad1e1e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201031/be543a47854c41f4b3e4d91d97674804.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201031/c5e5c367e0984cc7926e0aea1f441abf.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201031/bedb9f4081b24996b0774f9326eb61b7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201031/e605129345564bad87231fe30202b50f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201031/4e95d99c048846aaa23c6bfad909d315.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">店里颜值粉粉嫩嫩的<strong>桃花冰粉</strong>和<strong>桃花酿</strong>，女生来了都爱点。冰冰凉凉的冰粉刚好在吃过正餐后来一碗，甜汤<strong>由椰汁、甘蔗汁特调出来</strong>，清爽解辣~桃花酿酿好后<strong>直接从重庆空运到店</strong>，水蜜桃味，甜甜的~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201031/7d8eb1b6ea314a9bb84699203cac573c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>◈桃花浅浅等你来◈</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201031/70f011a244c0411aa023d5cc63026ff0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201031/51fa7230f6df4cf1bd57e07192f622d5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201031/e5de1f0c1aed470dbfb912cb2d0d204e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">和店名一样店里也是<strong>桃花主题</strong>，古香古色的装潢搭配粉嫩的桃花和粉色壁纸，颇有一番古韵</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201031/5dba612eb0fd4dfe85d3893363e59419.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201031/1cbc586c15174e8c9415f33b86d665a2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201031/ce8a604891aa46398240c6f890720f1f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">整个环境仙气飘飘，尤其适合古风拍照打卡，来这里拍美美的自带仙气打卡照，吃香嫩酸菜鱼，喝冰爽甜口桃花酿~快来！</p>
